{"tid":1195411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"TOTAL WAR(6月9) 陣列簡介","createTime":"2019-06-09T15:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T15:25:48.000Z","uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"73a3494fcc0913f682660e9ba708ed9207ec2572","tid":1195411,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xHugQsa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxHugQsa.jpg&h=2db99c71&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n前段矮石牆後有高鐵牆 間隔十分緊 固若金湯<br />\n有最精兵防守同樣是羅馬兵最佳出擊點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwfcoN1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdwfcoN1.jpg&h=76ca236c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中段高石牆後有高鐵牆 缺乏攻城兵器難以攻頂<br />\n以最少兵力守護已足夠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmDEOgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmDEOgq.jpg&h=05563c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尾段 有同是最精兵守尾門，但因鐵牆不足未能設置在全防線<br />\n有部份以矮鐵牆代替，石牆亦未及尾部，人員戰力比前段弱<br />\n視作只守不攻"}]}